    <p>The dynamic maps found throughout the website were designed and coded by Sean Gillies and Tom Elliott using the 
      <a href="http://leafletjs.com/">Leaflet Javascript map library</a>. User-selectable terrain layers are provided, including:</p>
    <ul>
